quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  24,11,"Pellet, …ďeen addu…ďe penaale …óen ko …ďe jamaa jeyaa…óo e moo…óon, wota on cikku …óum ko bone mo'on; ko woni …óum ko mo∆ī∆īere mo'on. No woodani kala ne…ó…óo immorde e ma…ď…ďe ko o faggitii kon e bakkaat, on fawtii…óo [bakkaat on] immorde e ma…ď…ďe, no woodani mo Lepte maw…óe."
  24,12,"Ko ha…óno oo tuma nde nan…óon …óum, wor…ďe gooŇč…óin…ďe …ďen e rew…ďe gooŇč…óin…ďe …ďen …ďe njananee ka wonkiiji ma…ď…ďe ko mo∆ī∆īi, …ďe mbi'a: "∆äum ko penaale …ďanngu…óe nii"."
  24,13,"Ko ha…óno ko nde …ďe ngaddata e …óum seedee…ďe nayo, si …ďe ngaddaani seedee…ďe …ďen; haray …ďeen …óon, to Alla ko kam…ďe ngoni fenoo…ďe …ďen."
  24,14,"Sinndo wonaano …ďural Alla ngal e yurmeende makko nden e dow moo…óon e aduna e yo La'akara Lepte maw…óe meematno on fii kon ko ukki…óon e muu…óum."
  24,15,"Tuma nde werlorayno…óon …óum …óenm…óe moo…óon, wowliron kunndu…óe moo…óon kon ko ganndal alana on e muu…óum sikkon …óum kadi ko newii…óum, hara non …óum ko mawnu…óom ka Alla."
  24,16,"Ko haanunoo tuma nan…óon nde, mbi'on: "Haanaa min nde min wowlata e dum, Senayee woodanii ma, …óum ko fenaande mawnde nii"."
  24,17,"Alla no waajaade on fii wota on fillo sugu [ndee fenaande] poomaa, si tawii on laatike gooŇč…óin…ďe."
  24,18,"Alla no …ďannginannde on Aayeeje …óen Alla ko O gandu…óo √Īee√Ī…óo."
  24,19,"Pellet, …ďeen yi…ó…ďe yo bone …óen sa'ako e [hoore] …ďen gooŇč…óin…ďe; no woodani …ďe Lepte muus…óe ka aduna e ka Laakara. Alla no Anndi, onon on nganndah."
  24,20,"Sinndo wonaano ∆Āural Alla ngal e dow moo…óon e Yurmeende makko nden e tawde pellet, Alla ko o Newii…óo jurmotoo…óo o."